# Vietnamese Sentiment Analysis

A Machine Learning project for classifying Vietnamese customer reviews into three sentiment categories:

* Negative (0)
* Neutral (1)
* Positive (2)

## Dataset

* ~31,000 Vietnamese reviews
* 3 sentiment classes
* Features: `content`, `label`, `star`

## Technologies

* Python
* Pandas
* Scikit-learn
* TF-IDF
* Joblib

## Project Structure

Vietnamese_Sentiment_Analyst/
│
├── data/
│   └── reviews.csv
│
├── models/
│   ├── model.pkl
│   └── tfidf.pkl
│
├── src/
│   ├── preprocess.py
│   ├── train.py
│   └── predict.py
│
├── utils/
│   └── io.py
│
├── main.py
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md

## Model Performance

| Metric         | Value  |
| -------------- | ------ |
| Accuracy       | 75.06% |
| Macro F1-Score | 0.63   |

## Installation

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Training

```bash
python main.py
```

## Prediction Example

```python
from src.predict import predict_sentiment

print(
    predict_sentiment(
        "Sản phẩm rất đẹp, giao hàng nhanh"
    )
)
```

Output:

```text
positive
```

